      <h1>map-pairs</h1>
      <p>Applies the function item <code>$f</code> to successive pairs of items taken one from
            <code>$seq1</code> and one from <code>$seq2</code>, returning the concatenation of the resulting sequences in order.</p>
      <p class="subhead">map-pairs($f as function(item(), item()) as item()*, $seq1 as item()*, $seq2 as item()*) &#8594; item()*</p>
